title: Rommel 2012.iso
description:
Rommel is a 2012 made for German TV movie about the last 7 month's of his life. Well written and well acted, It hasn't had well made English subtitles until now. Formated so you can burn it straight to one single layer DVD using Imageburn and enjoy. It is only made for American NTSC systems. Enjoy.


Director:
Niki Stein (as Nikolaus Stein von Kamienski)
Writer:
Niki Stein
Stars:
Ulrich Tukur, Tim Bergmann, Rolf Kanies
